[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Evaluating Java compiler settings**\n\nI'm considering a potential issue with AutoValue 1.4.1 and Java 21. It seems to support Java 8, but I might face a warning if I use the default source. To avoid this, I could specify -source 8 and -target 8. The JavaCompiler can work with source 8 on JDK21, but I need to ensure I include the classpath. I might use options like \"-proc:only\" and \"-classpath\" along with the system property for the class path.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_07e051bbc71ef92c0169f9c29d752881a18ad57b567f0bf898\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp-cKr5Li1HoK-S7Ek85GsiuXynBukh4KWRScKZW3H3zTr0Px9ynRMAmQ8jDIkpYWArbiPRcEPHfCWRPMkxOt3Opad4zeqvJ9NAxa9uMm2EVuQ8ShUvGU9Bh45CLa3p3Q5EcE-TpxN_xyX0B1rGK3AL27Ld8jm9iHI0VTn8Bq9ArN-m454twoLZu2Hi1yBOT5MZh-T8DPBWfUayIVYDMX5CjFZaqjYTCEbSBo9I4jhhRfGS-O2g5pqiBHxjSJ23SJXp2w5E1Vb6_jHAF8UBYvITDVu_i6WnxhKMp8Ha5_ZazpI_fP_WK_5xvKuXb7wfvX1Dwe-wv8eP2G9-ktoccWrwJUQtPSmQqfyS8M7vYYfeDE58ZiyWp40LX-TfPnLYHinHjTNBaHe9Nd-jmyNfI8bYZAgmL78CS1qq5pgfSP_nRPFkTMOEYtWhEwuqCCsfYTmJuHITmEdQbEmyUweiyZSaQfaXS6DV5agR9i-Vr2kvpMRHuyPPfabbMZdyiYFYqHg45WDX3poSmC2KR0jyLn7r3QggOPzJkq01iZSvqi8HHdqRkJPz5Tkt8uSBwkGDzZ8L6LBWntQHg9gKgBuYOGPTNonTkIILnj6rY7eBhG3R5-Y5uAjneJ3ZI2_D4K2P-ivA76aHIhbMA-oj1p1uU4X2dmRc2b5QWkIoXIHwpYi2UQJlV1hns2GBfE82tDNkUaOVMldEkDTbxRBQpDjh-pRgxkNopTVqpXtEZPPI7W5aMahrKK0i33e69b5Un0OaXbgfhVdy6flmNFl_EZAsmE0pEnYia7A9GyPUjXLnvBsy-twxkKn-fDD2ubUmZhY3aCx2Qkcs3nG9PLObM0DApW65narT5ONT2WAXIZvpHmHeymFZFkfbQgAaORFUA5iWjyDZ_-u-a0yQEwGhgzGF84i2l6-0_SWrEJkFKjGf5FeAAVPvP-HK5J7BSpIfPMuapTmsd5Yo_tVsVvf7tSwEXl3A9gI_mEGMJ4UXAi17kQc73P2wtyGq78r2RlcqJTMClS4gBL87AsbTJ7nJvDEYaB69nDFZNzC0L2v8X60x1eZ6OBKDyu9ynJA81pTZ8spw4Nvthd6Im9osqxwoChaCSRKEywKbdZl6PLtedbwInnk5FVygIcMk-tK5h0H0ckXlgXhpqhCWrPMVfKWKxnbBPLrVfT84iV8ITlF0lqKMxJ9JaK0ZVFz_FpZA704VeJ-jRU-NoaYvfw0q320mCxB_YL_oMquOIMbaH2wGXzwWEsJWKBGTainPHu_IbnOQ8GSWwiVJqYPkpHUEw